      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"act of defiance\" thing sounds exhausting though. Like, why bother fighting something that's literally built into the laws of physics? It feels like we're just performing this weird, painful play for no audience. If the end result is always going to be nothingness, then maybe there's actually more peace in just leaning into it instead of fighting it.",
